How to use the sounds 4 fl studio:
1 Paste and extract it to the desktop with winRAR or something, in a folder.
2 Run Fl studio
3 click options
4 click on file settings
5 then choose the folder
6 your sound-folder is now ''hiding'' over ''Misc'' in the fl studio browser...
